    <articleReference>
      <Value><![CDATA[Photochem Photobiol. 2011 Sep-Oct;87(5):1159-63. doi: 10.1111/j.1751-1097.2011.00968.x. Epub 2011 Aug 17.]]></Value>
    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Low-level laser therapy improves skeletal muscle performance, decreases skeletal muscle damage and modulates mRNA expression of COX-1 and COX-2 in a dose-dependent manner.]]></Value>
